step 1 : Configuring Git with username and email id: use below command 
syntax to config user name-----> $git config --global user.name "user_name"
example----> $git config --global user.name "28sanjayrp"

syntax to config user mail ----> $git config --global user.email "usermailID"
example ----> $git config --global user.email "sanjayrp8123@gmail.com"

step 2: validate or conform the user name nd email id: use below command
--->$git config --global user.name
--->$git config --global user.email

step 3: enabling the credentials storage globally: use below command
--->$git config --global  credential.helper store
